&lt;li&gt;Serve as the senior People Team leader in EMEA — owning the regional people strategy, representing the function to business leaders across the region, and ensuring that every aspect of the employee lifecycle operates with the same rigor and intentionality in Europe as it does in the US.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;General oversight for the people team including People Business Partners, Talent Partners and People Operations Partners in EMEA, providing the coaching, prioritization, and strategic context they need to operate at their highest level.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive execution of global People Team initiatives in EMEA — including performance management, pay transparency compliance ahead of EU regulatory deadlines, leadership competency framework rollout, and HRIS migration — adapting each for European legal, cultural, and operational realities.&lt;/li&gt;
